\newlabel{fig:baseline-summary}{{8}{9}{Baseline Monte Carlo summary for 1000 trials. The IEKF-fed correction shifts the terminal-miss distribution below the $10^{-3}\,\LU $ tolerance, retains a small median $\Delta V$ penalty, and remains statistically credible in both measurement space and state space}{figure.8}{}}
