\newlabel{fig:landmarks}{{15}{13}{L1 synthetic-landmark integration comparison, $n=1000$ trials per configuration, matched seeds across configurations. Boxes show terminal miss, position error at $t_c$, and the accepted-update fraction (any source) per scheduled epoch. Landmarks substantially improve the simulated bearing geometry; this experiment does not include real surface-feature identification}{figure.15}{}}
